humbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9JWcgG0.png&h=e13b654d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">袁澧林vs孫慧雪</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"95d7a61b593b78859c1bed500cbe0052c55c99b6","tid":355941,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b86f00d66b3bf7700168da9fbd56fa7e4d670fe","tid":355941,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/355899\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/355899</a><br />\n超聯已經喺較早前開賽,今晚可以投到合共17場賽事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b365295e8f870f6d007517502034d09ac87e904","tid":355941,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a773951f25265047a7763f7ee0088e44ab4088a5","tid":355941,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"投咗<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1ca683dc3c729f00c2a8cd2d2f5e6ee84a15a6","tid":355941,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img s